oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Work Camps for America pamphlet
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The pamphlet advertises a number of work camps across the country for the summer including at Highlander, Green Farms (Connecticut), West Park (New York), Goodrich Farm (Ohio), and Pacific Northwest (Oregon). Includes photograph and registration information for each camp.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Highlander Folk School (Monteagle, Tenn.); Work camps; Greens Farms (Conn.); Citizenship--Study and teaching; Rural conditions; Education; Labor movement; Miners; Hudson Shore Labor School; Factory laws and legislation
